translations.dashPassStrings_summerOfDashPassPromotio:
Get $0 delivery fees and an extra $10 off every week below
when you sign up for DashPass. Summer of DashPass delivers
the best food, drinks, and items you need from your
neighborhood, for less.

Free trial only available to new members who have not previously
redeemed free trial. Must be an eligible DashPass member using
weekly promo code in order to receive $10 off orders from select
eligible locations, or while supplies last at participating select
locations. Valid only on eligible DashPass orders on DoorDash from
select locations with a minimum subtotal, before taxes and fees,
equal to or greater than $20 for restaurants, convenience, gift
orders, pet supplies, and Pickup orders. $40 subtotal minimum
required for alcohol promo, only available in 18 states. $25
subtotal minimum required for all DashPass eligible grocery
orders. Offer not available for redemption on Caviar. Where
available, DashPass members who redeem offer for Pickup at
eligible, select store locations will not be awarded 5% credit
back in addition to $10 off promo. Fees (including service fee),
taxes, and gratuity apply. $0 delivery fees and 10% off due to
reduced service fees only apply when eligible order subtotal
minimum met on DashPass eligible orders. All orders subject to
availability. No cash value. Non-transferable.

translations.dashPassStrings_sodp_terms_body: Free trial only available to new members who have not previously redeemed free trial. Must be an eligible DashPass member using weekly promo code in order to receive $10 off orders from select eligible locations, or while supplies last at participating select locations. Valid only on eligible DashPass orders on DoorDash from select locations with a minimum subtotal, before taxes and fees, equal to or greater than $20 for restaurants, convenience, gift orders, pet supplies, and Pickup orders. $40 subtotal minimum required for alcohol promo, only available in 18 states. $25 subtotal minimum required for all DashPass eligible grocery orders. Offer not available for redemption on Caviar. Where available, DashPass members who redeem offer for Pickup at eligible, select store locations will not be awarded 5% credit back in addition to $10 off promo. Fees (including service fee), taxes, and gratuity apply. $0 delivery fees and 10% off due to reduced service fees only apply when eligible order subtotal minimum met on DashPass eligible orders. All orders subject to availability. No cash value. Non-transferable.

For your opt-out choice to be associated with your registered account, you’ll need to log in to your account and turn off personalization.

translations.packagePickupLandingHeadTitle: Package Pickup | UPS, USPS or FedEx Pickup | Doordash
translations.packagePickupLandingHeadDescription: With package pickup, you can request a Dasher to pick up your prepaid packages from wherever you are and drop them off at your local UPS, FedEx or USPS. Try it now!
translations.packagePickupLandingHeroSubtitle: With Package Pickup on DoorDash, you can request a Dasher to pick up prepaid packages from wherever you are and drop them off at a local UPS, FedEx, or Post Office (USPS).
translations.packagePickupHowItWorksTitle: Here's how Package Pickup on DoorDash works:
translations.packagePickupHowItWorks1: Set your pickup address, go to the carrier store page, and  provide details about your packages like  whether it requires a QR code or shipping label and how it's packed.
translations.packagePickupHowItWorks2: Prepare your packages for ASAP or scheduled pickup. Have a QR code? Send it to your Dasher via in-app chat.
translations.packagePickupHowItWorks3: Track your packages from pickup to drop-off. You’ll receive a photo of the receipt when the Dasher completes the drop-off.
translations.packagePickupUpsellTitle: Why should you use Package Pickup?
translations.packagePickupUpsellCaption1: From pickup to drop-off (with photo confirmation) in under 1 hour.
translations.packagePickupUpsellCaption2: {{flatAmount}} flat fee for up to 5 packages. Save {{saveAmount}} with DashPass.
translations.packagePickupUpsellCaption3: Track packages from pickup to drop-off. Contact us if anything goes wrong.
translations.packagePickupFeaturesTitle: Package Pickup for all your needs
translations.packagePickupFeature1: Same day pickup for your every need, wherever you are
translations.packagePickupFeature2: No shipping label? QR codes also work!
translations.packagePickupFeature3: Dasher will send a photo of the confirmation receipt after drop-off
translations.packagePickupQuestion1: Can I send items going to two different drop-off locations in the same request?
translations.packagePickupAnswer1: No. Each delivery request must be limited to a single drop-off point (a UPS, USPS, FedEx location). However, you may send up to 5 packages to the same drop-off location. If you decide to place more than one request to multiple drop-off locations, we recommend you physically write the drop-off location on each package.
translations.packagePickupQuestion2: Can DoorDash print a label for me?
translations.packagePickupAnswer2: No, DoorDash will not print the label for your package return. Labels must be pre-printed and pre-attached to the package you intend to return for it to be eligible for this service.
translations.packagePickupQuestion3: How will I know that my package has been dropped off? Can I receive a tracking number?
translations.packagePickupAnswer3: The Dasher will send a photo confirmation of your package at the drop-off location, and the app will notify you once the package has been dropped off. DoorDash will not provide tracking numbers.
translations.packagePickupQuestion4: Will this service process my refund for me?
translations.packagePickupAnswer4: No. This service only completes the first stage of your return; picking up your package and dropping it off to FedEx, USPS, or UPS. To get information on your refund, please contact the online retailer you purchased from.
translations.packagePickupQuestion5: What happens if my package(s) are never delivered?
translations.packagePickupAnswer5: If you suspect your package has not been dropped off, please contact DoorDash Customer Support at +1(855) 213-2693 or through the Help Support Button in-app. Our team will investigate the incident and you may be subject to reimbursement for the value of your packages, up to {{amount}} per order. Please see the Package Reimbursement section for more details.

translations.seo_faq_answer_1: DoorDash connects you with the best nearby restaurants. Use the DoorDash website or app to browse eligible restaurants. Order and securely pay online and your food is on the way! You can even track your delivery right to your door. Getting your favorite foods delivered is that easy.
translations.seo_faq_question_2: Can I schedule a delivery in advance?
translations.seo_faq_answer_2: Yes. Before clicking Place Order, simply select Scheduled and you can select the date and time you wish to have your meal delivered. After selecting the date and time you want, click Place Order and we'll handle the rest.
translations.seo_faq_question_3: How fast will I get my food?
translations.seo_faq_answer_3: How fast you'll get your food depends on a number of things. How far is the restaurant? How bad is traffic? Is it snowing out? The average time is approximately 40 minutes but it could be more or less. Either way, you can track where your driver is on the DoorDash website or app.
translations.seo_faq_question_4: What is a group order and how can I create one?
translations.seo_faq_answer_4:
A group order allows multiple people to add items into an order at the same time. Once a group order is created through a DoorDash Account, the rest of the group doesn't need to have a DoorDash Account to use the group order link. Even better, you can pre-order up to four days in advance, which makes it great for events and meetings.

Follow these steps to create a group order:


  1. Log into your DoorDash account.
  2. Choose your restaurant.
  3. In the upper right-hand corner, click Create a group order.
  4. Send the group order link to others.
  5. When everyone is done adding their items into the cart, you can close the group order and complete checkout.
.

translations.referral_terms_title: DoorDash Customer Friends and Family Referral Program Terms and Conditions
translations.referral_terms_p1: Existing customers ("Referrer") who refer friends and family as new customers ("Customer") to the DoorDash platform, may be eligible to receive referral credits (“Credit(s)”). Customer must sign up using the unique link ("Link") provided to them by Referrer. The Link must be provided to Customer through email, text, or the Share Your Link option on the app. Referrer is prohibited from posting referral links on sites including, but not limited to Google, Craigslist, Twitter, RetailMeNot and other similar publicly accessible sites. DoorDash reserves the right to deactivate or invalidate any Credits obtained through these channels.
translations.referral_terms_p2: Referrer will only receive Credits for the first 25 Customers they refer that are located in the same country as the Referrer (i.e. a Referrer in the United States cannot successfully refer a Customer in Canada). Customer will receive one Credit when they sign up through the Link, are one of the 25 Customers, and meet the requirements as indicated in the offer. DoorDash reserves the right to deactivate or invalidate any Credits obtained by either Customer or Referrer in excess of these amounts. Credit amounts vary based on regions, and Referrer location will determine the application region and Credit amount. Credit amounts will be stated in Referrer's DoorDash account and in the offer received by Customer. Select regions require a minimum subtotal (excluding taxes and fees) on Customer's first order that must be met in order for both Customer and Referrer to receive Credits. Customer will be disqualified and will not receive Credits if DoorDash determines that Customer has previously created a DoorDash account. DoorDash reserves the right to withhold or invalidate Credit obtained through the DoorDash Friends and Family Referral Program if DoorDash determines or believes that the Credit was received through error, fraudulent, illegal, or in violation of these terms and conditions or any other applicable agreement between you and DoorDash.
translations.referral_terms_p3: Credits will be applied automatically at checkout to order amount (excluding gratuity). Credits cannot be applied to alcohol products. Credits can only be redeemed for DoorDash orders on DoorDash.com or on the DoorDash app with the latest version, and within DoorDash service areas and delivery hours. Credits cannot be redeemed for cash or cash equivalent. Credits are not transferable and may not be auctioned, traded, bartered, or sold. Credits may not be used in conjunction with select promotions. DoorDash reserves the right to withhold or invalidate Credit obtained through the DoorDash Friends and Family Referral Program if DoorDash determines or believes that the Credit was received through error, fraudulent, illegal, or in violation of these terms and conditions or any other applicable agreement between you and DoorDash. DoorDash is not a retailer or seller. Subject to change by DoorDash at any time. Void where restricted or prohibited by law. Customers who refer or plan to refer more than 50 individuals can contact referral-affiliates@doordash.com to enter the DoorDash affiliate program to receive credit after receiving credit for referring 25 individuals to DoorDash.
